name: OpenSea

display.label: Approval For All
display.description: ApprovalForAll event is emitted when the approval status for an operator for a given owner changes.

operation.signature: event ApprovalForAll(address indexed account, address indexed operator, bool approved)

inputFields.label: Account
inputFields.helpText: account: The address of the account that owns the tokens.

inputFields.label: Operator
inputFields.helpText: operator: The address of the account that is approved or disapproved.

inputFields.label: Approved
inputFields.helpText: approved: A boolean indicating whether the operator is approved or disapproved.

display.label: Creator Changed
display.description: This event is triggered when the creator of an item is changed.

inputFields.label: Id
inputFields.helpText: The ID of the item that had its creator changed.

inputFields.label: Creator
inputFields.helpText: The new address of the creator.

display.label: Meta Transaction Executed
display.description: This event is emitted when a meta transaction is executed.

operation.signature: event MetaTransactionExecuted(address userAddress, address relayerAddress, bytes functionSignature)

inputFields.label: User Address
inputFields.helpText: The address of the user who initiated the meta transaction.

inputFields.label: Relayer Address
inputFields.helpText: The address of the relayer who executed the meta transaction.

inputFields.label: Function Signature
inputFields.helpText: The function signature of the meta transaction.

display.label: Ownership Transferred
display.description: This event is emitted when ownership of the contract is transferred from one address to another.

operation.signature: event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)

inputFields.label: Previous Owner
inputFields.helpText: The previous owner's address

inputFields.label: New Owner
inputFields.helpText: The new owner's address

display.label: Paused
display.description: This event is triggered when an account is paused.

inputFields.label: Account
inputFields.helpText: The address of the account that was paused.

inputFields.label: Value
inputFields.helpText: The value for which the permanent URI is set.

inputFields.label: Id
inputFields.helpText: The ID of the value.

display.label: Transfer Batch
display.description: This event is emitted when a batch of tokens is transferred from one address to another.

operation.signature: event TransferBatch(address indexed operator, address indexed from, address indexed to, uint256[] ids, uint256[] values)

inputFields.label: Operator
inputFields.helpText: The address of the operator performing the transfer.

inputFields.label: From
inputFields.helpText: The address from which the tokens are being transferred.

inputFields.label: To
inputFields.helpText: The address to which the tokens are being transferred.

inputFields.label: Ids
inputFields.helpText: An array of token IDs being transferred.

inputFields.label: Values
inputFields.helpText: An array of corresponding token values being transferred.

display.label: Transfer Single
display.description: This event is triggered when a single token is transferred from one address to another.

inputFields.label: Operator
inputFields.helpText: The address of the operator performing the transfer.

inputFields.label: From
inputFields.helpText: The address from which the token is being transferred.

inputFields.label: To
inputFields.helpText: The address to which the token is being transferred.

inputFields.label: Id
inputFields.helpText: The unique identifier of the token being transferred.

inputFields.label: Value
inputFields.helpText: The amount of tokens being transferred.

display.label: URI

inputFields.label: Value
inputFields.helpText: The URI of the item. (string value)

inputFields.label: Id
inputFields.helpText: The ID of the item. (uint256 indexed)

inputFields.label: Amounts
inputFields.helpText: An array of corresponding amounts of tokens to be transferred.

inputFields.label: Data
inputFields.helpText: Additional data to be passed to the receiving contract, if any.
